    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>HospiceLink CRM — We Market Plus LLC | Last Updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect information you provide directly to us when you use HospiceLink CRM:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name, email address, organization name, and password (stored as a bcrypt hash — we never store your actual password)</li>
    <li><strong>CRM data:</strong> Prospect records, referral source information, clinical notes, family communication logs, and mileage data that you enter into the system</li>
    <li><strong>GPS/Location data:</strong> Approximate location captured when a note is synced or a mileage trip is logged (Max and Gold tiers)</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Login timestamps, feature usage, and audit log entries (Gold tier)</li>
    <li><strong>Payment information:</strong> Processed entirely by Stripe — we never see or store your full credit card number</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide, maintain, and improve the Service</li>
    <li>To send you transactional emails (account creation, password reset, billing notifications)</li>
    <li>To send weekly performance reports to account admins (Max and Gold tiers)</li>
    <li>To respond to your support requests</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations, including HIPAA where applicable</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>We do not sell your data. We do not use your data for advertising. We do not share your data with third parties except as described in this policy.</strong></p>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We share data only with the following service providers who process it on our behalf:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — Payment processing. Subject to Stripe's Privacy Policy.</li>
    <li><strong>SendGrid (Twilio)</strong> — Email delivery for account and notification emails.</li>
    <li><strong>Render</strong> — Cloud hosting and database infrastructure. Data stored in the United States.</li>
    <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude AI)</strong> — AI assistant features. Your CRM data context is sent to Anthropic's API to generate responses. Anthropic does not train on your data per their API terms.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All data is transmitted over HTTPS/TLS encryption</li>
    <li>Passwords are hashed using bcrypt (never stored in plain text)</li>
    <li>Authentication uses JWT tokens with expiration</li>
    <li>Role-based access controls limit what each user can see</li>
    <li>Gold tier includes a full HIPAA audit log of all system access</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>See our full retention schedule in the Terms of Service. Summary:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Marketing records: 3 years active, archived up to 7 years</li>
    <li>Clinical notes and family communications: 7 years minimum (HIPAA)</li>
    <li>HIPAA audit logs: 6 years minimum</li>
    <li>Mileage/GPS: 4 years (IRS/DOL)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access:</strong> You may export all your data from the Admin section at any time</li>
    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> You may edit any record in the CRM directly</li>
    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Marketing data may be deleted by your admin. Clinical data is subject to HIPAA retention requirements</li>
    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Data export available as CSV from your Admin panel</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use only essential cookies necessary for authentication (JWT session tokens stored in localStorage). We do not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies.</p>

  <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>The Service is not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

  <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We will notify you by email at least 14 days before any material changes to this policy take effect.</p>

